{"title":"Java设计模式：策略模式","uid":"2fcc47af7e967abfb1d26d14cdced0c8","slug":"Java-DesignPattern8","date":"2020-04-16T00:14:53.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:41:30.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Java-DesignPattern8.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"什么是策略模式\"><a href=\"#什么是策略模式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"什么是策略模式\"></a>什么是策略模式</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Strategy模式也叫策略模式是行为模式之一，它对一系列的算法加以封装，为所有算法定义一个抽象的算法接口，并通过继承该抽象算法接口对所有的算法加以封装和实现，具体的算法选择交由客户端决定（策略）。Strategy模式主要用来平滑地处理算法的切换 。</p></blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"实现步骤\"><a href=\"#实现步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实现步骤\"></a>实现步骤</h2><ul>\n<li>新建Strategy接口<pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public interface Strategy &#123;\n    public void encrypt();\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n<li>创建策略（算法）的具体实现。\u000b<pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public class MD5Strategy implements Strategy&#123;\n\n\t@Override\n\tpublic void encrypt() &#123;\n        System.out.println(&quot;MD5加密&quot;);\n\t&#125; \n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n<li>创建策略的外部封装类，或者说策略的容器类。根据不同策略执行不同的行为。策略由外部环境决定。 </li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public class Context &#123;\n    private Strategy strategy;\n\n\tpublic Context(Strategy strategy) &#123;\n\t\tthis.strategy &#x3D; strategy;\n\t&#125;\n    public void encrypt()&#123;\n        this.strategy.encrypt();\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>在main方法中使用<pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public class MainClass &#123;\n    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;\n        Context context &#x3D; new Context(new MD5Strategy());\n        context.encrypt();\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n","text":"什么是策略模式 Strategy模式也叫策略模式是行为模式之一，它对一系列的算法加以封装，为所有算法定义一个抽象的算法接口，并通过继承该抽象算法接口对所有的算法加以封装和实现，具体的算法选择交由客户端决定（策略）。Strategy模式主要用来平滑地处理算法的切换 。 实现步骤 新...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":872,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":13,"path":"api/categories/Java.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":25,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"